## Recommended Frontend Flow

### Student Flow
```
Signup → POST /auth/signup
Login  → POST /auth/login
Submit profile → POST /profile/submit
Upload resume  → POST /profile/{user_id}/resume
Trigger analysis → POST /profile/{user_id}/analyze
Create session → POST /session/create
WebRTC handshake → WS /session/{id}/signal
Live call → WS /session/{id}/stream
End call → POST /session/{id}/end
```

### Admin Flow
```
Login → POST /auth/login
Dashboard overview → GET /admin/analytics
All leads → GET /admin/leads
Lead detail → GET /admin/leads/{user_id}
Session report → GET /admin/sessions/{session_id}/report
Manual notify → POST /admin/notify/{user_id}
```
